cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.PL 

The paper deals with formalizing knowledge-based systems, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves knowledge representation and schema/ontology matching, which are relevant to logic (cs.LO) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses modular knowledge representation, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and the use of inference rules, which is relevant to programming languages (cs.PL).
